item.title: About
item.description: This is the personal website and blog of Carlos Rey, a software engineer in Brooklyn, NY. I figured I needed a place to put everything that’s going through my head. Don’t expect regular updates, or interesting content. In fact, this site is not written for you, so please don’t read it.
